description: Two sperm whales in the ocean discuss the logistical challenge of consuming college students. One whale asks another, named Eddie, to consider how many students they could eat at once. The scene presents a surreal situation where marine predators contemplate humans as prey, injecting dark humor through the absurdity of the specific query regarding quantity.
caption: "Gee, I don't know, Eddie ... how many college students do you think you could eat at one time?"
